snippet: Yaya Toure slammed home a penalty and Kelechi Iheanacho netted a simple goal for Manchester City as they secured a 3-0 win at struggling Hull City who again came up empty-handed despite a battling display on Monday....
lead_paragraph: Yaya Toure slammed home a penalty and Kelechi Iheanacho netted a simple goal for Manchester City as they secured a 3-0 win at struggling Hull City who again came up empty-handed despite a battling display on Monday.

headline.main: Man City Go Second With 3-0 Win Over Hull
headline.print_headline: Man City Go Second With 3-0 Win Over Hull
